      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCELZI (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (23.35) last time in a Novice race at this track. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Better than last start and worth following up. NIGELLA GUNDI (4) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 1.3 lengths from the winner (17.81). Expected to run well. MILWAUKEE MATES (1) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 6 lengths at this track (17.54) beating I'm Jazzy in a Maiden on January 1. One of the better hopes. LINDY DOLL (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
